home.safety.what.message: DigiQuip is the hub that easily connects your machinery and equipment fleet with available documentation, inspection procedures, safety training, and specific machine and equipment training.
home.safety.what.description: The description of the safety section on the home page

home.safety.how.message: -So that the right people use the right machine in the right way.
home.safety.how.description: The how part of the description of the safety section on the home page

home.safeuse.title.message: Correct use of equipment depends on the necessary training and competence
home.safeuse.title.description: The title of the safe use of machinery section on the home page

home.safeuse.arg1.message: DigiQuip is a technology company that simplifies the management of competence, training, and documentation. We offer unique solutions for conducting equipment-specific training, also known as type training or machine-specific training. In addition, our solutions can be used to keep track of courses, competence certificates, project experience, and education.
home.safeuse.arg1.description: The first argument of the safe use of machinery section on the home page

home.safeuse.arg2.message: At the construction site? By scanning a QR code or another identifier, individuals receive instant confirmation of whether they have the appropriate and necessary documented training to use that specific machine, tool, or safety equipment. Reporting or completion of training can be done immediately. This ensures that the right people use the right equipment in the right way.
home.safeuse.arg2.description: The second argument of the safe use of machinery section on the home page

home.safeuse.arg3.message: By placing QR codes on machines or equipment, users gain immediate access to their own competency status for the specific work equipment.
home.safeuse.arg3.description: The third argument of the safe use of machinery section on the home page

home.consolidate.title.message: Full control over equipment and documentation
home.consolidate.title.description: The title of the consolidate your training section on the home page

home.consolidate.arg1.message: Inspections, documents, and user manuals for equipment should always be easily accessible when needed. Why? This makes it easier to ensure that equipment is well-maintained and only used when it is safe to do so.
home.consolidate.arg1.description: The first argument of the consolidate your training section on the home page

home.consolidate.arg2.message: At the construction site? When a worker or inspector scans the equipment's identifier, they can find the latest inspection status, documents, and user manual. Additionally, a pre-use inspection can be quickly carried out and documented, either with or without a digital checklist.
home.consolidate.arg2.description: The second argument of the consolidate your training section on the home page

home.consolidate.point1.message: Digital checklists for machines and equipment.
home.consolidate.point1.description: The first point of the consolidate your training section on the home page

competence.banner.title1.description: The title of the competence page part one

competence.banner.title2.description: The title of the competence page part two

competence.banner.title3.message: Competence is important for progress and safety.
competence.banner.title3.description: The title of the banner(image) competence page part three

competence.banner.arg1.message: Competent individuals are trained in the proper use of tools and equipment, reducing the risk of accidents and injuries associated with improper handling. Therefore, it is important that employers have an overview and provide necessary training when needed.
competence.banner.arg1.description: The first argument of the competence progress and safety section on the competence page

competence.banner.arg2.message: DigiQuip is a comprehensive competence solution that is particularly well-suited for those working with equipment. Our platform makes equipment training easy, and in addition employers can keep an overview of various competence such as education and experience.
competence.banner.arg2.description: The second argument of the competence progress and safety section on the competence page

competence.practical_training.title1.description: The title of the practical training section on the competence page

competence.practical_training.title2.description: The second title of the practical training section on the competence page

competence.practical_training.arg1.message: DigiQuip offers end-to-end solutions for equipment-specific training, and we are committed to making this easy to implement when needed. Additionally, you will have an overview of other safety training (competence certificates and courses), qualifications, and project experience.
competence.practical_training.arg1.description: The first argument of the practical training section on the competence page

competence.practical_training.arg2.message: Training should be tailored to each individual employee and depends on both motivation and experience. As a user of DigiQuip, equipment-specific training can take place as e-learning or practical training. Practical training means that the training is provided by someone knowledgeable to one or more others. The benefits of practical training are numerous, but we would like to highlight two: social and active. Participants can ask questions and test the specific machine or equipment along the way, which is beneficial for both social interaction and active learning.
competence.practical_training.arg2.description: The second argument of the practical training section on the competence page

competence.practical_training.img_descri.description: The description of practical training image in practical training section on the competence page

competence.digital_training.title.description: The first title of the digital training section on the competence page

competence.digital_training.arg1.message: Employers must always provide the necessary training. For equipment that requires particular caution during use, training must always be given prior to use. This training is referred to as equipment-specific, type training, machine-specific, and more.
competence.digital_training.arg1.description: The first argument of the digital training section on the competence page

competence.digital_training.arg2.message: DigiQuip is a comprehensive solution for equipment-specific training. As an employer, you have control over when training is required, and employees can complete their training either practically or digitally. While the training is taking place, it is documented and stored. In a dedicated dashboard, you can keep track of all training in real-time.
competence.digital_training.arg2.description: The second argument of the digital training section on the competence page

competence.digital_training.img_descript.description: The description of digital training image in digital training section on the competence page

workequipment.banner.arg1.message: When a business manages many machines and equipment, it is important that documents, manuals, and reports are organised and readily available when people need them.
workequipment.banner.arg1.description: The first argument of the work equipment banner

workequipment.banner.arg2.message: Most machines and equipment requires inspections, and this must happen in a timely manner. The inspection of work equipment can be streamlined using digital checklists with standard reporting. Digital checklists for machines and equipment make it easier to carry out and document everything from pre-use to annual inspections.
workequipment.banner.arg2.description: The second argument of the work equipment banner

workequipment.systematized_documentation.description: The title of the systematized documentation section in the work equipment page

workequipment.systematized_documentation.message: DigiQuip is the hub that easily connects your machinery and equipment fleet with available documentation and control procedures. By collecting and centralising all documents and information in one place, you save time and money.
workequipment.systematized_documentation.description: The first argument of the systematized documentation section in the work equipment page

workequipment.systematized_documentation.message: And not least, employees no longer have to repeat the same tasks multiple times, which is beneficial for the working environment.
workequipment.systematized_documentation.description: The second argument of the systematized documentation section in the work equipment page

workequipment.machines_equipment.arg1.message: In DigiQuip, you can keep track of the latest status and necessary inspections, ranging from annual to pre-use and maintenance inspections.
workequipment.machines_equipment.arg1.description: The first argument of the machine equipment section in the work equipment page

workequipment.machines_equipment.arg2.message: For example, if a pre-use inspection of the work equipment is to be conducted, the worker will see this when they scan the QR code or other identifier on the equipment. The person will find the option to confirm or go through a relevant checklist while this is documented. As the machine owner, you can find all history and details for each individual piece of work equipment.

aboutus.banner.title2.message: Through years of building a rental business, Lars saw a clear need to improve safety for customers.
aboutus.banner.title2.description: The second title of banner section in the aboutus page

aboutus.banner.arg1.message: Incorrect use of equipment is potentially very risky and can lead to serious injuries, or, in worst case, even death. The lack of easily accessible and structured product information, as well as limited collaboration in the industry, held back improvement in safety.
aboutus.banner.arg1.description: The first argument of the banner section in the aboutus page

aboutus.banner.arg2.message: The need was clear – to offer the industry a solution that centralizes content for rental companies and businesses, in cooperation with dealers and OEMs, and make this information easily accessible to equipment users.
